headline: Goldman Leads Dow Jones As These Financial Firms Break To New Highs
summary: Goldman Sachs stock jumped more than 4% Monday afternoon, making it the largest contributor to the Dow Jones Industrial Average's 1.6% afternoon gain.

summary: PNC Financial is driving growth via acquisitions and partnerships, from a FirstBank deal expanding Colorado to a Coinbase tie-up enabling Bitcoin trading.

headline: PNC Completes Acquisition of FirstBank
summary: The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc. (NYSE: PNC) today announced that it has completed its acquisition of FirstBank Holding Company, including its banking subsidiary, FirstBank, following receipt of all required regulatory approvals and satisfaction of customary closing conditions. The transaction further advances PNC's strategic growth strategy and expands the bank's presence across high-growth communities in Colorado and Arizona.

headline: PNC Declares Dividend of $1.70 on Common Stock
summary: The board of directors of The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc. (NYSE: PNC) declared a quarterly cash dividend on the common stock of $1.70 per share. The dividend will be payable Feb. 5, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business Jan. 20, 2026.
